snippet.title: Is Johnny winning the public opinion? // #justiceforjohnny update
snippet.description:
This video is an update on recent happenings of the Johnny Depp vs amber heard situation. I do give my opinions on some of the things but please make sure to do your own research. It is important for this situation to not make speculations from what others say. 

I do not profit from putting up my opinions and I am not a bot. I am against abuse, no matter the gender. I support #JusticeforJohnny because I have read the evidence and I see that amber’s allegations are false. Sign the petition to have her Removed from Aquaman 2. Please do not harass amber heard. 

https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

Subpoena order links: 

https://www.fairfaxcounty.gov/circuit/sites/circuit/files/assets/documents/pdf/high-profile/depp%20v%20heard/cl-2019-2911-def-memo-supp-mot-compel-docs-resp-to-rev-8th-req-10-16-2020.pdf

https://www.fairfaxcounty.gov/circuit/sites/circuit/files/assets/documents/pdf/high-profile/depp%20v%20heard/cl-2019-2911-order-attys-fees-11-23-2020.pdf
